--- 
title     : Ruby Applets
summary   : Dedicated Ruby Command System
license   : Apache 2.0
contact   : trans <transfire@gmail.com>

requires:
  - path
  - plugin
  - facets
  - syckle (build)

authors:
  - Thomas Sawyer

description:
  Ruby Applets creates an isolated namespace for running ruby-based 
  commands. Think of it as a secondary system `bin/` designed for
  Ruby developers, but integerated with-in the Ruby language.

